thread.title: BRIEF-Capitaland Commercial Trust Posts Qtrly Net Property Income of S$68 MLN

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Capitaland Commercial Trust Posts Qtrly Net Property Income of S$68 MLN
text:
Jan 25 (Reuters) - Capitaland Commercial Trust:
* 4Q DPU 2.083 CENTS VERSUS 2.39 CENTS * QTRLY NET PROPERTY INCOME S$68 MILLION, DOWN 4 PERCENT * Q4 GROSS REVENUE S$86.3 MILLION VERSUS S$89.7 MILLION * LOWER NET PROPERTY INCOME IS EXPECTED IN FY 2018 AT SOME CCT PROPERTIES
* THERE WILL BE FLOW- THROUGH FROM NEGATIVE RENT REVERSIONS OF LEASES COMMITTED IN 2017 INTO 2018 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
